00:00:43,534 --> 00:00:51,176
game was, and all the content and everything. So right on Bungling Bay would have fit in

8
00:00:51,176 --> 00:00:52,896
that little box over there.

9
00:00:52,896 --> 00:00:58,598
Now this is what the actual original looked like, back from 1984. It was my first game.

10
00:01:00,025 --> 00:01:02,346
It was very interesting, kind of, the learning I went through on this.

11
