00:56:06,547 --> 00:56:07,668
Three months, three months.

1109
00:56:07,668 --> 00:56:09,269
And these were good games.

1110
00:56:09,269 --> 00:56:10,149
They weren't junk.

1111
00:56:10,149 --> 00:56:13,411
They were just amazing little pieces of craftsmanship

1112
00:56:13,411 --> 00:56:13,931
on the Apple II.

